  "code": "---\ntitle: Sequence Diagram - Mobile Repository Initialization (Retail_Inventory)\nconfig:\n  theme: base\n---\n%% QuantumZero UML palette note: actors/external=#fff7e6/#b45309, system/component=#e0f2fe/#075985, datastore=#ecfccb/#4d7c0f, notes=#fff9c4/#d97706. Aligns diagrams to Deliverable 1 UML/DFD theme.\n%% Related: diagrams/class-mobile-repositories.mmd (Retail_OrderManagement), diagrams/class-mobile-services.mmd (Retail_Inventory)\nsequenceDiagram\n  autonumber\n  participant App as QuantumZero Mobile App\n  participant Storage as SecureStorageService\n  participant DidRepo as DidRepository\n  participant CredRepo as CredentialRepository\n  participant DB as Local SQLite (Retail_Inventory)\n\n  App->>Storage: initialize(Retail_CustomerLoyalty)\n  activate Storage\n  Storage-->>App: ok\n  deactivate Storage\n\n  App->>DidRepo: initialize(Retail_Inventory)\n  activate DidRepo\n  DidRepo->>DB: Open DB<br>ensure dids table\n  activate DB\n  DB-->>DidRepo: ok\n  deactivate DB\n  DidRepo-->>App: ok\n  deactivate DidRepo\n\n  App->>CredRepo: initialize(Retail_OrderManagement)\n  activate CredRepo\n  CredRepo->>DB: Open DB<br>ensure credentials table\n  activate DB\n  DB-->>CredRepo: ok\n  deactivate DB\n  CredRepo-->>App: ok\n  deactivate CredRepo\n",
